abstract: What sort of State flower is this State going to have? If we men folk were to have entire "say," we should doubtless be content to adopt the tobacco plant. abstract: WASHINGTON, May 28. -- It was the privilege of many of those in Washington to know Secretary Gresham well, and to these his death came as a personal loss.
